headline: Are Wall Street Analysts Predicting C.H. Robinson Stock Will Climb or Sink?
summary: Over the past year, C.H. Robinson has modestly underperformed the S&P 500 Index, while Wall Street analysts maintain a fairly bullish outlook on its growth prospects.
